metadata.description:
Inspired by the Culture of "GM" lead by @CozomoMedici at #HouseofMedici and @rata_yonqui's very unique infusion of the LITizen culture, "LITizen I: GM" collection was born, marking this collection the first ever gesture of gratitude outside of the LIT administration, by LITizen to LITizens, in celebration of the LIT culture. 
A hint of continuity has been left in the name of the collection. This collection is the beginning of a movement that will unfold to the wildest of our imagination.
Together we will pave the way to the future of culture, art and entertainment.
By 0xBlock
Twitter @blockmidas
metadata.name: GM 1
